Subject: [PATCH] fix-c11-flag

---
 configure                           | 16 ++++++--------
 libavcodec/arm/mpegvideo_arm.c      |  8 ++++++++
 libavcodec/ccaption_dec.c           |  8 ++++++++
 libavcodec/version.c                |  9 +++++++++
 libavdevice/version.c               |  9 +++++++++
 libavfilter/version.c               |  9 +++++++++
 libavfilter/vf_yadif_videotoolbox.m |  9 +++++++++
